title: Tara Nikkel and the Shaman of La'la Eek
description: Tara Nikkel is back in an all new afterlife adventure. A rift in the fabric that holds the universe together threatens the destroy the stability of our world. The Guild calls upon Tara Nikkel to return to the really real world and face a powerful shaman who stands between the Black City and earth. This new installment is full of adventure, monsters, and more fun than ever! Ages 13+
author: R.A. Sapp
